{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id5a12689d-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s49g"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"49g"},"text":"§ 49g.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" State plans","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Any State desiring to receive assistance under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t29/s49e"},"text":"section 49e of this title","children":[],"tail":" shall prepare and submit to, and have approved by, the Secretary and the Secretary of Education, a State plan in accordance with section 3112 or 3113 of this title."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id5a12689e-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1933-06-06/ch49/s8"},"text":"June 6, 1933, ch. 49, § 8","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/48/115"},"text":"48 Stat. 115","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1954-08-03/ch655/s6/b"},"text":"Aug. 3, 1954, ch. 655, § 6(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/68/665"},"text":"68 Stat. 665","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/300/tVI/s601/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–300, title VI, § 601(d)","children":[],"tail":", formerly title V, § 501(d), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-10-13"},"text":"Oct. 13, 1982","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/96/1395"},"text":"96 Stat. 1395","children":[],"tail":"; renumbered title VI, § 601(d), "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/628/tVII/s712/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–628, title VII, § 712(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", (2), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-11-07"},"text":"Nov. 7, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/3248"},"text":"102 Stat. 3248","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/220/tIII/s306"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–220, title III, § 306","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-08-07"},"text":"Aug. 7, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/1081"},"text":"112 Stat. 1081","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/128/tIII/s306"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–128, title III, § 306","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-07-22"},"text":"July 22, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/1627"},"text":"128 Stat. 1627","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id5a12689f-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id5a1268a0-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id5a1268a1-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2014—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/128"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–128","children":[],"tail":" amended section generally. Prior to amendment, section consisted of subsecs. (a) to (d) relating to submission, required content, and approval of State plans."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1998—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/220/s306/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–220, § 306(1)","children":[],"tail":", amended subsec. (a) generally. Prior to amendment, subsec. (a) read as follows: “Any State desiring to receive the benefits of this chapter shall, by the agency designated to cooperate with the United States Employment Service, 